targets.query: SELECT min(min), max("max"), sum("sum") / sum(cnt) AS avg, sum("cnt") AS "count" FROM "rpc_method" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY "method", "topic", "process_name", "endpoint"
SELECT sum("cnt") FROM "rpc_method" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(30s), "process_name"
SELECT sum("sum") / sum(cnt) as avg  FROM "processing_delay" WHERE "process_name" =~ /^$process_name$/ AND "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "process_name"

panels.title: delay between message receiving and dispatching to the method

targets.query: SELECT sum("sum") / sum(cnt) AS avg FROM "reply_delay" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "process_name" =~ /^$process_name$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "process_name"
